            div.Intro.container
                h1 WELCOME TO BETTER HOLIDAYS
                p Better Holidays has been creating dream holidays for over 25 years. If you’re searching for a romantic getaway, honeymoon, cruise, a business trip or you just want a fabulous family holiday, we’re here to make your trip easy and memorable.
                p Our expert, multi-award winning team will ensure your holiday is exactly what you want, providing in-depth travel knowledge, personal recommendations and the best possible price. So go on… discover something new!
