            div.topPicks
                h1 Top Picks
                .Picks
                    .itemPicks
                        div#Sorrento.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 Sorrento
                            p Located in Campania, Southern Italy, Sorrento is a town characterized by beautiful architecture and many restaurants and cafes as well as shops that mainly cater to tourists.
                            img(src="Images/sorrento.jpg")
                        div#CaribeanIslands.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 Caribbean Islands
                            p Tourism is the main economic booster of the Caribbean. All of its islands have their own specialties to offer such as sailing, scuba diving, swimming with dolphins and surfing.
                            img(src="Images/CaribeanIslands.jpg")
                            div.onHover
                        div#SanFrancisco.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 San Francisco
                            p It is hard to imagine how a compact city like San Francisco can house a multitude of attractions raging from scenic natural wonders to highly-preserved Victorian architecture.
                            img(src="Images/SanFrancisco.jpg")
                        div#LakeLouise.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 Lake Louise
                            p Alberta, Canada is blessed with natural wonders, one of which is the Alberta Rockies Region where the world-famous Banff National Park sits.
                            img(src="Images/LakeLouise.jpg")
                        div#London.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 London
                            p London is one of the most visited capitals in Europe, with visitors from across the globe keen to get a glimpse of its many famous sights.
                            img(src="Images/London.jpg")
                        div#Singapore.item
                            div.onHover
                            h1 Singapore
                            p Singapore is a famous port city well known for its roles it plays in the global economy especially in Asia. Singapore is also a title of a country and of course its capital city is the port city of Singapore. 
                            img(src="Images/Singapore.jpg")
